Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2A2D90&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Showdown!\NKing Dark Versus X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Closed for the day, call 0499 487...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Noda Sachiko. She's\Na student of the late Dr. Nanbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A student of Nanbara's? Then maybe\Nshe has a piece of the blueprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If she does, you must beat the X Rider to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This sounds like a job for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then begin at once, Ant Capone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sì, King Dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your coffee, daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a good girl, Nanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised mommy I'd look\Nafter you until she got back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to see Mrs. Noda, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko's away! What do you want with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The blueprint Dr. Nanbara gave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Why don't you tell me where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Blueprint...? I don't know! And\NI don't know where Sachiko is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot... What husband doesn't\Nknow where his wife's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Out with it. Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, anyway!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ant Capone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now talk! Talk! Where's Sachiko gone!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your mommy gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy's gone to Nasu View Hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl! And you can come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it! Hurry, hurry!\NA little faster, Chiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One more length, Chiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Keisuke! Phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-The phone?\N-It's a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Jin Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A blueprint from Dr. Nanbara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the Nanbara Group. We decided to\Nhand it over as soon as we heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll meet you right away, but...\NHow will I recognise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:06:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll be wearing a red flower.\N-Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Noda Sachiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to collect you. Please get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-Sorry, I'm Tachibana Toubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you run that coffee shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's right. Now--\N-Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough messing around...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are the ones\Nwho aren't going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD must be chasing their tails right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-You underestimate GOD!\N-A GOD monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Toubei, be a good\Nslave and drive like I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A red flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they must've--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the boss isn't back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not in his room, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, listen. There's a homing device in the\Nchief's bag. Use that to contact him, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the blueprint and you're free to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look around, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one of my ants can hypnotise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But all of them together can drain the blood from your body in seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk! Where's the blueprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-I-it's--\N-Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And curse you too, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still get the blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey, where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko's safe. Probably back at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been five hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she got scared\Nand went back to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone would do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't just quit if she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she's that naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll only be safe once they\Nhave her piece of the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You think she might hand it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For Mr. Jin Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Invitations to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Invitations?\N-Invitations!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Awesome!\N-Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The history of the Japanese usage of the Swahili\Nterm "jambo" is too complex to fit here, but rest\Nassured you're not about to see a spelling mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jambo African Show!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, everyone, to the Nasu View Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We hope you enjoy the Jambo African Show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, without further ado, let's go! Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she ever serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you'd join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd be stand out less in a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even GOD wouldn't show up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's the blueprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll take this!\N-Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you get for ruining our show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-You should run.\N-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get this blueprint to Mr. Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...You could give it to me instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the blueprint if you value Nanae's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanae!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In my handbag...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've got one chance:\NBring it to me yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll trade you Nanae for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But look, come alone, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nanae!\N-If I see Jin Keisuke, Nanae's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you alright?\N-We got your bag back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can you give us the blueprint now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, but... I misplaced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But you were just gonna\Ngive us something out of your bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I assumed I would be safe if\Nthey thought I'd given it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please forgive me.\N-Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD probably think you've\Ngiven us the blueprint, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing for you to worry about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know where it is,\Nthen there's nothing to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my daughter is waiting\Nat home. I should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we take you to the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be alright by myself, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Where's my daughter?\NWhere's Nanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At the top. C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanae is safe, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit babbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nanae!\N-Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The blueprint comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!? You promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You only get one chance at tricking GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can die together, mother and child!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider! How did you find us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Sachiko changed her\Nmind too quickly, so I followed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're too late, X\NRider! I've got the blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you now? Are you sure\Nit's not a fake again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Run!\N-Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacuum Hell Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider! King Dark will triumph in the end!\NAll of those blueprints will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold my majestic form!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to someday crush you\Nwith these very hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The terrible giant, King Dark,\Nhas challenged me himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark has finally appeared before the X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Will even the X Rider be\Nable to defeat this colossus?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(50,0)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl appears in Keisuke's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When her angelic face becomes that of a GOD\Nmonster, Toubei plunges into a deep valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode,\Nfeaturing Riders #2 and V3:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Terror! King Dark's Vengeance!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.53,0:23:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
